sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant Database
    participant LearningSystem

    User->>Frontend: Request learning materials
    Frontend->>Backend: Get materials request
    Backend->>Database: Query learning content
    Database-->>Backend: Return content data
    Backend->>LearningSystem: Process materials
    LearningSystem-->>Backend: Processed materials
    Backend-->>Frontend: Learning materials response
    Frontend-->>User: Display materials

    Note over User,Frontend: User interaction phase
    Note over Backend,Database: Data retrieval phase
    Note over LearningSystem: Content processing

    alt Materials available
        Backend->>Frontend: Send materials
        Frontend->>User: Display content
    else No materials found
        Backend->>Frontend: Send error message
        Frontend->>User: Show "No materials available"
    end

    loop For each material
        User->>Frontend: Select material
        Frontend->>Backend: Load material details
        Backend-->>Frontend: Material content
        Frontend-->>User: Show material
    end
